<h1> Here is your workout progress so far: </h1>


<h2> Your total amount lifted (in pounds) is: {{totalVolume}} </h2>
<h2> Your average RPE is: {{averageRPE}} </h2>

<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <ul>
      {{#each exercises}}

        <div class="col-sm-4">
          <li> Exercise Name: {{name}} </li>
          <li> Number of Reps: {{reps}} </li>
          <li> Number of Sets:{{sets}} </li>
          <li> Weight: {{weight}} </li>
          <li> RPE: {{rpe}} </li>
          <li> Date: {{date}} </li>
          <br>
        </div>
      {{/each}}

    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<h1> Total Experience Points Earned: {{experience}} </h1>

<svg class="top-middle" width="1000" height="50">
  <rect width={{experience}} height="100" style="fill:rgb(10,70,200)" />
</svg>


<h2 class = "progress"> You are currently level: {{level}} </h2>

<h2 class = "progress"> Your height is {{height}} inches. </h2>
<h2 class = "progress"> Your weight is {{weight}} pounds. </h2>


<h2 class = "progress"> Your BMI is {{bmi}}. </h2>
<h2 class = "progress"> You are {{difference}} pounds away from your goal weight </h2>
<h2 class = "progress"> You have to eat {{dailyCals}} fewer/greater calories each day to gain/lose that amount in a month. </h2>


<h3 id="avatar-desc"> Your Character Avatar: </h3>

<img src={{icon}} id="icon" height="100" width="100">
